{"tid":1610341,"cid":5,"subCid":12,"title":"全民無·限·期罷工罷課，救自己、救義士！迫政府讓步！（長文,亦請文宣入）","createTime":"2019-10-01T17:08:21.000Z","updateTime":"2019-10-07T16:08:43.000Z","uid":271434,"like":90,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":47,"replies":[{"pid":"95bb692c7f51a3c8226b815d80ca44e2deaa16a9","tid":1610341,"uid":271434,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-10-01T17:08:21.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">今日政府宣布，香港各區發生暴動！</span><span style=\"color: gold;\">亦即係話，今日只要出過街嘅非警察人士，都有機會告你參與暴動</span>！<span style=\"color: red;\">要去狗屋坐48個鐘美，而且定罪嘅話一坐就幾年</span>！<br />\n<br />\n打工反學嘅你，為你自己將來，呼籲大家，<span style=\"color: red;\">盡快組織無限期罷工、罷課</span>！<span style=\"color: gold;\">只有咁，先可以癱瘓社會運作，直到政府宣布徹底妥協，答應五大訴求為止！</span><br />\n<br />\n罷工，你可能面對被炒魷魚嘅風險，但罷工不需要附上刑責！警察唔可能上門捉你返工！<span style=\"color: red;\">只要齊心，換來嘅係政府徹底讓步！大家包括今日有出街嘅人亦唔會被告暴動！警察亦可以立即停止暴力，義士亦可以沉冤得雪</span>！<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: gold;\">如果大家唔齊心罷工，有一日警察會上門捉你，告你暴動！就算唔係，警察以後亦會變本加厲，用更重手對付大家！以後大家無機會出聲！</span>今日見到已經開槍謀殺義士！我地一定要立即制止納粹警暴歪風！請大家立即籌備無限期罷工、罷課！<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<strong>請文宣幫手將以上論點製作poster廣傳，多謝各位</strong></span>"},{"pid":"96dddf4200929c4c4eedbc94a892fef1647ee2e3","tid":1610341,"uid":259329,"like":8,"dislike":0,"score":8,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-10-01T17:09:00.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"1509c69477ee6f3e4996af3715c7d13b4dee0251","tid":1610341,"uid":256281,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-01T17:09:35.000Z","msg":"唔好同我講乜野罷工！同我入黎我解釋你聽<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1609904\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1609904</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區"},{"pid":"b107eafeded1c3ff76c06fbe1057f8162a35cb32","tid":1610341,"uid":271434,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-01T17:12:46.000Z","msg":"煽動開槍嘅員佐級協會主席林志偉應負全責，同埋應將全隊警隊擺落美國制裁名單！<br />\n<br />\n解散警隊，重新招募方法<br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1591746\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1591746</a><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n今日香港慘劇係雜種一手造成：<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\">有明確訊息證實係習近平一人當日堅持拒絕「撤回」及下令將44人極速起訴暴動！</span><br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1602129\" target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1602129</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區"},{"pid":"8d582f24d13f503af7a208c79742c09633804add","tid":1610341,"uid":279235,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-10-01T17:20:48.000Z","msg":"P牌冇人理，哀莫大心死<br />\n<br />\n全部睇晒佢！記住喺心！識得點做！<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1609844\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1609844</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區"},{"pid":"7d977bbec8130f7d04e6c1ad0e412a1117ddbbcc","tid":1610341,"uid":273218,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-01T17:31:43.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://lihkg.com/thread/1451065/page/1\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lihkg.com/thread/1451065/page/1</a>"},{"pid":"83059f9d132f1ab1fdfd956d4490a3dfdff088b3","tid":1610341,"uid":176484,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-01T17:43:49.000Z","msg":"Push"},{"pid":"c6360669fa49dfaad6f2da80d631091da8a86b17","tid":1610341,"uid":233180,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-01T17:51:34.000Z","msg":"p"},{"pid":"be9a61e9df214786df24e9e749a649602ca889c4","tid":1610341,"uid":205378,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-01T17:52:10.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><strong><span style=\"color: blue;\">麻煩有時間入黎睇睇<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></span></strong></span><br />\n【長文】✰✰ 一個港島街坊有野想同今日港島班前線講 ✰✰<br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1610354\" target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1610354</a>"},{"pid":"3cf82742070c185e168b80d5ac4fe37a8bbb9e00","tid":1610341,"uid":271434,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"8d582f24d13f503af7a208c79742c09633804add","tid":1610341,"uid":279235,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-10-01T17:20:48.000Z","msg":"P牌冇人理，哀莫大心死<br />\n<br />\n全部睇晒佢！記住喺