1610341,"uid":25425,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-10-02T01:24:43.000Z","msg":"係香港咁特別 琴日打仗今日返工"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-02T02:47:28.000Z","msg":"如果尋日落過街嘅，真係要籌備罷工，因為政府已經定性暴動，好快就會大規模捉人<br />\n只有無限期罷工先可以迫政府讓步，救返自己，否則最終自己都係俾人捉而無咗份工"},{"pid":"2e406a470bc9ced059371471ec3d8a2252c68a05","tid":1610341,"uid":170577,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-02T03:32:40.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"144ba7b2ad7a87cb9a1da221050740d029abe25c","tid":1610341,"uid":20091,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-02T03:34:35.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"fde22151be767acdf54604b84eccb300544818ac","tid":1610341,"uid":270398,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-02T03:38:21.000Z","msg":"今日開槍打前線, 好快就會亂打街坊, 望下TG就知"},{"pid":"c2cd22ff8f7f9fe5c94c2981c96b89731fa23c16","tid":1610341,"uid":247940,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-10-02T03:53:36.000Z","msg":"叫香港人三罷難過登天<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\nSorry for失敗主義"},{"pid":"5b0d43b8d5da6032b2be6267739a79758d815f52","tid":1610341,"uid":271434,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"c2cd22ff8f7f9fe5c94c2981c96b89731fa23c16","tid":1610341,"uid":247940,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-10-02T03:53:36.000Z","msg":"叫香港人三罷難過登天<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\nSorry for失敗主義"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-02T04:03:19.000Z","msg":"今次事件嚴重過85，政府已經講咗尋日各區發生暴動，只要在有關地區出現過，都可以告暴動，政府睇返閉路電視就可以捉人，被捕後份工都會無埋<br />\n<br />\n罷課方面成本更低。<br />\n<br />\n不過我唔同意罷市，始終香港租金昂貴，但希望老闆體諒罷工員工。幫個體戶打工嘅，如果老闆係黃絲，亦盡量唔好罷工"},{"pid":"ab123254e10914f8584f8578a5aad6a9854ee8f2","tid":1610341,"uid":238919,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-02T05:10:46.000Z","msg":"點解冇人推"},{"pid":"f415fad84ab60c94524f072fe0bf74c8df95d9f1","tid":1610341,"uid":238919,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-10-02T05:10:56.000Z","msg":"推啊"},{"pid":"9dfa799c1dad80d338e5195ad9f820c47cdb1321","tid":1610341,"uid":271434,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"f415fad84ab60c94524f072fe0bf74c8df95d9f1","tid":1610341,"uid":238919,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-10-02T05:10:56.000Z","msg":"推啊"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-02T05:12:03.000Z","msg":"多謝。希望大家積穀防饑，準備長期大罷工"},{"pid":"2e844c471b99e7fe91b7b097b4e831ac19ad3d63","tid":1610341,"uid":108831,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-10-02T05:13:26.000Z","msg":"罷工可以癱瘓社會運作 但點解要罷課 學生嘅姿態仲表明得唔夠清楚咩"},{"pid":"c66794c3b0c4ab2ea4787bb061e644e12d1985b0","tid":1610341,"uid":271434,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"quote":{"pid":"2e844c471b99e7fe91b7b097b4e831ac19ad3d63","tid":1610341,"uid":108831,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-10-02T05:13:26.000Z","msg":"罷工可以癱瘓社會運作 但點解要罷課 學生嘅姿態仲表明得唔夠清楚咩"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-02T05:14:48.000Z","msg":"罷課成本最低，同埋令更多仲係中立嘅人去搵真相"},{"pid":"a5315d7c5a9dae5f5a297a4a9bf6cc03ceedf46b","tid":1610341,"uid":103598,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-02T05:32:25.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"7213afc8f2a5d40d3a7dd940308e1ec0de0648ed","tid":1610341,"uid":24160,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"2df5304fc5eebe97149b337d389841eeb34adb50","tid":1610341,"uid":271434,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"